Let \{\mathcal {F}_{i}\}_{i\in  I} be a family of groups. We define the Product Group \prod _{i\in  I}\mathcal {F}_{i} whose underlying set is the product of the underlying sets of the family, where the binary operator is defined by, for any g,h\in  \prod _{i\in  I}\mathcal {F}_{i},
